{"word":"διαφανής","slug":"διαφανής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαφανής</b></el> adj (diafa^n hs_es suff_acc) <p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>διαφαίνομαι</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>seen through, transparent</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>red-hot</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>transparent, manifest, distinct</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-νῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>famous, illustrious</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}